{"tid":410451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解港鐵要賠","createTime":"2017-09-23T02:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T01:08:37.000Z","uid":81684,"like":34,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6588b288f7b9e6628b742302e28347b8ab28d46","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"賠係人情 唔賠係道理<br />\n港鐵無責任去賠比傷者<br />\n更何況港鐵都係受害者<br />\n雖然啲女傷者好慘<br />\n但港鐵都唔係善堂<br />\n個個喺入面比第三方整親又喊賠同大陸人有咩分別<br />\n港鐵唔係出於同理去賠嘅話嗰500萬心諗當比乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765a6316464cb861413662a384ea00dc803de0bf","tid":410451,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"大陸人拎綜援都用緊香港人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比外人就得 <br />\n比自己人就唔得"},{"pid":"8502d759e523ea73170ac490e6c2cb7625e9f1ad","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人拎綜援都用緊香港人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比外人就得 <br />\n比自己人就唔得</blockquote><br />\n比自己人都唔係呢啲case吓嘛<br />\n呢啲叫比乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6262212a5fde78720c7facba407fc79eb6965ec2","tid":410451,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"唔係&quot;賠&quot; 係捐"},{"pid":"f9ec53789eeab4fc5c30737f1f8093b46ff2a4e0","tid":410451,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"法理上港鐵如果冇 negligence 就唔洗賠<br />\n但人情上作為咁大間機構<br />\n呢件事又咁大單<br />\n唔涼薄嘅馬屎坑係唔係應該要捐少少出嚟？"},{"pid":"63002f4c46838f3aa12add5c0bdd613261ede916","tid":410451,"uid":135491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"上市公司怕咩比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f219122a2539ffbcd9edb4cf058c15bc47e4ac","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上市公司怕咩比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最怕做壞規舉<br />\n收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abe482d1ac04dc3630208a89d32e7b3b443b170","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係&quot;賠&quot; 係捐</blockquote><br />\n港鐵用個賠字都算比足面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151a3e27d2e07e75ff9647d226629f250fbf61a6","tid":410451,"uid":31939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"其實&quot;捐&quot;少少錢挽救下港鐵個公眾形像有咩唔好<br />\n咁簡單既公關技巧都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8e471563ac191561065f2e11b56b159c5941b9","tid":410451,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"好簡單啫，佢平時加價自都剩係講佢嗰套無認受性嘅道理（可加不減機制）<br />\n咁市民自然唔會同佢講道理。"},{"pid":"7e2921717565935d6753518f85d4b589136afc70","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法理上港鐵如果冇 negligence 就唔洗賠<br />\n但人情上作為咁大間機構<br />\n呢件事又咁大單<br />\n唔涼薄嘅馬屎坑係唔係應該要捐少少出嚟？</blockquote><br />\n惻隱之心嘅嘢<br />\n人地有心嘅話一早衝出嚟捐<br />\n真係涼薄嘅話咁大間公司要滅聲都仲得<br />\n捐錢本來就你情我願<br />\n港鐵最後&quot;賠&quot;五球都算係咁<br />\n仲可以話今次係個別例子 下不為例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a21a27d1f5721ce8faecc0d94272afebcde0499","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實&quot;捐&quot;少少錢挽救下港鐵個公眾形像有咩唔好<br />\n咁簡單既公關技巧都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開波就咁順攤以後咪比人當老奉當善堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知大陸人幾鐘意喊賠<br />\n加上香港人都有蝗化嘅跡象<br />\n港鐵夠遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96977739199c44e5cb18b6a64c0480aadcbed4d1","tid":410451,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"去到邊都係你咁既"},{"pid":"f6bad8695742807d6dab174113b2b12b8749746e","tid":410451,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c62e30267d0c884d8c3c7acc43c4592ffe1bfee","tid":410451,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"因為你係大公司，做野唔係剩計&ldquo;要定唔要&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdc026c6cc7535a8fec3f3869d305910563ea7c","tid":410451,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"如果佢純私人公司就話啫<br />\n<br />\n但佢起野，佢啲地前前後後幾多係靠政府<br />\n<br />\n咁就係要有埋社會責任"},{"pid":"6b855daf96709e2d97c554e3c760a5069b343d37","tid":410451,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"希望你下次坐港鐵平平安安啦"},{"pid":"3ee499e5293a8c4f313147a105dfcf8b3de0db3b","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 冇做好安檢，居然有人帶到危險物品上車困獸鬥<br />\n2. 作為運輸公司利用上蓋物業賺巨富，應該盡社會責任</blockquote><br />\n好多地方嘅列車都無人安檢 做起上嚟都好麻煩 香港人又難服侍 所以無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國呢啲case都係政府發放恩恤金同賠償㗎喎<br />\n因為人地賺得多就要擔起社會責任同有錢人一定要捐錢有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea69503764c69903de4ac9d628f478e645390c5","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望你下次坐港鐵平平安安啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔坐公交 你先要平安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0d2ab63823a352ee9f86a1ad950b266b42aee9","tid":410451,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上市公司怕咩比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最怕做壞規舉<br />\n收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收唔收得返都唔關你事啦 你去唔到呢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1440f4c0f63407ecf59bbfb01300878a3d4e23d","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢純私人公司就話啫<br />\n<br />\n但佢起野，佢啲地前前後後幾多係靠政府<br />\n<br />\n咁就係要有埋社會責任</blockquote><br />\n根本政府就要衝出嚟負責<br />\n睇吓搞到而家幾撚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a1d35c0a94d73d52455ea61cd23d686a223618","tid":410451,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf61a9869a298d5369a41d540478ccb538270c42","tid":410451,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢純私人公司就話啫<br />\n<br />\n但佢起野，佢啲地前前後後幾多係靠政府<br />\n<br />\n咁就係要有埋社會責任</blockquote><br />\n特權謀利機構"},{"pid":"88bcb3e11de0c5e6ab35207ec0aea342ef9275f4","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上市公司怕咩比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最怕做壞規舉<br />\n收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收唔收得返都唔關你事啦 你去唔到呢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做壞規舉收唔返呢句又傷害到你呀？"},{"pid":"5da127c5e200f8865b9a8dd5d3f67bab5eee73d7","tid":410451,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"唔係賠 係公關"},{"pid":"c005a41b2d216c7439433f6b90f806ec8b65fcbd","tid":410451,"uid":2126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗"},{"pid":"cadd8dfec447c185c4b42c3357eeb8747c77f831","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私底下賠簽保密協議可唔可行？</blockquote><br />\n呢啲表面嘢本來就政府做<br />\n私下做有咩意義"},{"pid":"10ca47fe9d6f7677e5dd0cb611a6ebb4037bea4d","tid":410451,"uid":62259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實&quot;捐&quot;少少錢挽救下港鐵個公眾形像有咩唔好<br />\n咁簡單既公關技巧都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n救左個形象有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n形象差唔差對佢都冇影響"},{"pid":"0227961aee3a3344dc716c9e6812e406b52e926f","tid":410451,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>希望你下次坐港鐵平平安安啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔坐公交 你先要平安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公交你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8768e51222e22b93a27c7d439e6856808ff05250","tid":410451,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上市公司怕咩比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最怕做壞規舉<br />\n收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收唔收得返都唔關你事啦 你去唔到呢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做壞規舉收唔返呢句又傷害到你呀？</blockquote><br />\n想提你無需諸事姐 港鐵夾硬加價咁多年都夠膽死 賠錢嘅野佢會有蝕底嘅話公眾壓力根本迫唔到 唔洗你個蟻民擔心"},{"pid":"c8ff86948de03cc143444ec0902a4de11c776d5b","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>希望你下次坐港鐵平平安安啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔坐公交 你先要平安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公交你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔坐小巴巴士的士地鐵<br />\n得未呀你老母"},{"pid":"18af2e8090e42bce4f6ef230ac9582fb5fdeb643","tid":410451,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n袋落我地袋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比5球你代佢地受傷好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84760ddef5dd6fcf73b7a022922628988c4e8a10","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n袋落我地袋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比5球你代佢地受傷好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講緊要求賠償嗰班呀"},{"pid":"994379ccddf06661c9c2c4316698f0e20958bdd5","tid":410451,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n邊個收唔重要<br />\n最緊係狗鐵嘔出黎<br />\n<br />\n我就咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fe0e910ee5c7b544a69237f5c1960ef62a9382","tid":410451,"uid":3304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"因為你呢啲港豬只會從利益出發，下下講錢<br />\n而作為一個發達城市，好多事要考慮道德層面，<br />\n你諗下受害者無辜俾燒除咗搵港鐵幫仲可以點？<br />\n賠定捐只係文字遊戲，但一間大公司絕對有責任幫受害者"},{"pid":"263a7eb0b46e5ee23c38e7657dfb685024cdcc29","tid":410451,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n袋落我地袋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比5球你代佢地受傷好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講緊要求賠償嗰班呀</blockquote><br />\n佢地無受傷會賠比佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650a4c3a050d087cf5ede88c596f30cebe339cfb","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個比唔重要<br />\n最緊要係有錢袋<br />\n<br />\nD人係咁諗</blockquote><br />\n袋落我地袋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比5球你代佢地受傷好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講緊要求賠償嗰班呀</blockquote><br />\n佢地無受傷會賠比佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地講緊咩你都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c706f8fc8f4a1ec9e0ac36a4aa013247247879","tid":410451,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你呢啲港豬只會從利益出發，下下講錢<br />\n而作為一個發達城市，好多事要考慮道德層面，<br />\n你諗下受害者無辜俾燒除咗搵港鐵幫仲可以點？<br />\n賠定捐只係文字遊戲，但一間大公司絕對有責任幫受害者</blockquote><br />\n我上面咪講咗<br />\n呢啲意外正常都係政府衝出嚟做<br />\n點解唔係話政府涼薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e9a027e3bd04a02db6376b05e2b38f31d24ef9","tid":410451,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06a8857069d5d10300cb0223c93a94b6b2023317","tid":410451,"uid":37941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"比少少錢出黎又改善下個形象<br />\nwhy not?"},{"pid":"24d64fffc2ea6bbff04a9fe52af0b933feddce16","tid":410451,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4031300c5eb5e06f1d45aa843f91cd18a3c2339","tid":410451,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法理上港鐵如果冇 negligence 就唔洗賠<br />\n但人情上作為咁大間機構<br />\n呢件事又咁大單<br />\n唔涼薄嘅馬屎坑係唔係應該要捐少少出嚟？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔叫賠，安慰金或恩恤都好，錢係用黎塞住人把口"},{"pid":"744b6a1e84966204cf56dac10c23bdbc86e80f25","tid":410451,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76175fb49c72a8fe5a369dad978794c986457204","tid":410451,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實&quot;捐&quot;少少錢挽救下港鐵個公眾形像有咩唔好<br />\n咁簡單既公關技巧都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本唔洗挽救<br />\n形像差唔會少左人搭"},{"pid":"e76fbd1c14192b6fd49737b09b0c50759b726039","tid":410451,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 冇做好安檢，居然有人帶到危險物品上車困獸鬥<br />\n2. 作為運輸公司利用上蓋物業賺巨富，應該盡社會責任</blockquote><br />\n好多地方嘅列車都無人安檢 做起上嚟都好麻煩 香港人又難服侍 所以無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國呢啲case都係政府發放恩恤金同賠償㗎喎<br />\n因為人地賺得多就要擔起社會責任同有錢人一定要捐錢有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都估到會講外國case<br />\n外國鐵路唔蝕都偷笑，仲有好多係私營<br />\n香港唔止賺大錢，仲要政府係股東，完全係兩回事"},{"pid":"6d94e2e33e008de14adb390f871949d83adeaa6b","tid":410451,"uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"港鐵形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n形象好又點 差又點<br />\n只要列車準時 班次足<br />\n你會唔會因為港鐵形象而選擇唔搭<br />\n<br />\n我唔否認可能會有人咁做<br />\n但我可以肯定十個人裏面 九個人都應該唔會改變乘車習慣<br />\n<br />\nBTW 如果呢單野港鐵要賠錢<br />\n咁前排巴士上比人隊死果個女仔 家人都應該獲賠償<br />\n同理 總之以後發生乜野事都好<br />\n就算唔係服務提供者問題<br />\n都應該要賠啦<br />\n<br />\n講到最後 我只係要問一個問題<br />\n點解而家有人要求港鐵就事件賠償<br />\n<br />\n一個字 錢"},{"pid":"f5a4223a338f8a2f93b51da1ce5acc415d8000b9","tid":410451,"uid":121060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n形象好又點 差又點<br />\n只要列車準時 班次足<br />\n你會唔會因為港鐵形象而選擇唔搭<br />\n<br />\n我唔否認可能會有人咁做<br />\n但我可以肯定十個人裏面 九個人都應該唔會改變乘車習慣<br />\n<br />\nBTW 如果呢單野港鐵要賠錢<br />\n咁前排巴士上比人隊死果個女仔 家人都應該獲賠償<br />\n同理 總之以後發生乜野事都好<br />\n就算唔係服務提供者問題<br />\n都應該要賠啦<br />\n<br />\n講到最後 我只係要問一個問題<br />\n點解而家有人要求港鐵就事件賠償<br />\n<br />\n一個字 錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多香港人同大陸人一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93639bae521156844a538caf44694b68c962fb0","tid":410451,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ee93e6dd460d7c943a7653f0a05c31cc4f6f88e","tid":410451,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人拎綜援都用緊香港人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比外人就得 <br />\n比自己人就唔得</blockquote><br />\n完全歪曲事實，你咁講不如大家入庫房拎啦，破壞法治精神由你蝗做起。"},{"pid":"9029ee12330db452ad1679cc911b648ddb2d8088","tid":410451,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 冇做好安檢，居然有人帶到危險物品上車困獸鬥<br />\n2. 作為運輸公司利用上蓋物業賺巨富，應該盡社會責任</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返大陸返傻咗你？巴士斬人你有無講呢句？<br />\n<br />\n作為咩公司有咩問題，問題係拎地既方式，賺物業錢有邊個無靠交通？盡社會責任係咪咁盡都有問題啦"}]}